- CSSContainerRule: `/workspace/components/script/dom/css/csscontainerrule.rs` (lines 40-51)
- CSSMediaRule: `/workspace/components/script/dom/css/cssmediarule.rs` (lines 43-54)
- CSSSupportsRule: `/workspace/components/script/dom/css/csssupportsrule.rs` (lines 42-56)

#### 3. **Update Pattern Duplication**

The `update_rule()` methods follow a consistent pattern:
```rust
pub(crate) fn update_rule(&self, {rule}: Arc<{RuleType}>, guard: &SharedRwLockReadGuard) {
    self.cssconditionrule.update_rules({rule}.rules.clone(), guard);
    // CSSMediaRule has additional medialist update logic
    *self.{rule_field}.borrow_mut() = {rule};
}
```

