- CSSMediaRule: `/workspace/components/script/dom/css/cssmediarule.rs` (lines 78-85) - with additional medialist update
- CSSSupportsRule: `/workspace/components/script/dom/css/csssupportsrule.rs` (lines 63-71)

#### 4. **SpecificCSSRule Trait Implementation - Boilerplate**

